      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, totally ready for many more adventures. It runs great and has been well-loved over the years. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I'm super happy to chat and want to make sure you feel great about your new car!",
