    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2006 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution IX MR is a mechanically robust example of the final 4G63-powered generation. It features the MIVEC-equipped turbocharged 2.0L inline-four, delivering power through a 6-speed close-ratio manual gearbox and a sophisticated Active Center Differential (ACD) with three selectable modes. The chassis remains taut, supported by factory-spec Bilstein monotube dampers and Brembo four-piston calipers for superior thermal management during spirited driving. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and an ACD pump pressure check. This vehicle offers exceptional turn-in response and linear power delivery, making it an ideal candidate for a purist seeking a driver-focused platform.",
