      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and value, maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity and aesthetic cleanliness. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is pristine and smoke-free; the leather seats remain soft and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver's bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the dual-zone climate control and the upgraded infotainment system. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive folder of service receipts. We recently performed an oil service and installed a fresh set of tires, ensuring this car is ready for the road immediately. It drives straight, brakes firmly, and offers the composed ride quality you expect from a well-cared-for machine. This is a solid, honest example that will serve its next owner reliably for years to come.",
